content:
Je že komu ratalo instalirat? 

Najdu sem tale navodila:
 




	
	
		
		
			Citat:
 How to install Garmin Mobile XT on Windows CE core 5.0
------------------------------------------------------

Just a few steps:

1. Install on SD card via ActiveSync the installer from the folder "GarminMobileXTforWM_41040w-installer". In the case of errors, please ignore them.
2. Overwrite on your SD card in the directory Garmin/Apps/WM/ using files in the folder "GarminMobileXTforCE-patch"
3. Run QUE.exe application
4. Jump to Settings -> About.
5.  Make note of your "Card ID"
6.  Launch the keygen, and type in your "Card ID" into the "Unit ID" field.
7.  Select "Garmin Mobile XT" in the Sotware Product drop-down box and hit Generate button.
8.  Copy (CTRL+C) your generated device unlock key to the clipboard.
9.  Now open the Notepad and paste (CTRL+V) the key and save the file as SW.UNL
10. Put your newly created file to your SD Card\Garmin directory and restart GMXT.

Unlocking allows you to use internal built GPS.
Enjoy!


best regards

Ciang Li Quien

Telezzo MediaTeam
		
		Klikni za razširitev
	

Men se ustavi že pri instalaciji. Naprava je tuševa, z WIN CE 5.0, activesync kaže da je povezan, setup od Garmina pa ne najde naprave.
